⸻

❌ Common Issues & Fixes

Issue	Solution
Domain not resolving	Check DNS records & wait
Cannot add domain	Upgrade App Service Plan
HTTPS not working	Bind SSL certificate
CI/CD not triggering	Check GitHub Actions logs

⸻

🧹 Cleanup

az group delete --name elearning-rg --yes --no-wait

